\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Most nursery rhymes were not first sung by children, but are vestigial remains of once popular ballads and folksongs, of forgotten street cries and passion plays, of long outdated prayers and proverbs. }
